lead_paragraph: Start-ups and big companies alike have tried to take on Google by building a better search engine. That they have failed has not stopped brave new entrants.
snippet: Blekko aims to show search results from only trustworthy sites, weeding out sites filled with little relevant information.

headline.main: A New Search Engine Says Less Is More
